Package: stats2data
Title: Data Simulation from Summary Statistics
Version: 0.0.1.000
Date: 2025-06-27
Authors@R:
    person(c("Sebastian", "A.", "J."), "Lortz", , "s.a.j.lortz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-0281-7996"))
Description: We introduce stats2data: A Nonparametric Approach to Data Simulation from Summary Statistics. The primary scope of this algorithmic framework is to simulate complete raw datasets using only summary statistics, giving researchers a way to generate plausible sample data when original data are unavailable.
